@{"XRefAttrs" link XRefAttrs.guide/main}       @{TAB} changes attributes of one or several xref file(s)

@{"XRefConvert" link XRefConvert.guide/main}     @{TAB} converts AutoDoc or C Include files to AmigaGuide
                @{TAB} files

